                      margin: 0 0 0 0;">
              Une collaboration
            </p>
            <p style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 36px;
                      font-style: italic; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.2;
                      margin: 0 0 0 0;">
